cc:Work.dc:title: Green Cube
cc:Work.dc:description: This building is a cube of a size 12x12x12 meters. The connecting part of the building is the communication knot with staircases, elevators and WC’s. There is a recreation zone on the roof top. The diagonal glass openings on the main and the back facade create the dinamic composition. The composition of the side facades is created by the granith masses with greenery and glass. The static composition of side facades opposes the dinamic of the main one. The house that was suppose to be artificial looks authentic for the natural environment.
